paragraphs.title: Digital Marketing
paragraphs.text:
%md

### Situation:

- A fast food company has created three seperate promotions online to attempt to garner more business. They allow there seperate locations to choose which promotion to run and are curious after looking at there results which promotion was the best for the different markets where the fast food restaurant is located. 
- This sql notebook is an attempt to analyze that data set

msg.data:
Situation:

  • A fast food company has created three seperate promotions online to attempt to garner more business. They allow there seperate locations to choose which promotion to run and are curious after looking at there results which promotion was the best for the different markets where the fast food restaurant is located.
  • This sql notebook is an attempt to analyze that data set

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands), week
from marketing
group by week, locationid
;
paragraphs.title: Overall Perfomance through the Month

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands)
from marketing
group by locationid
order by sum(salesinthousands) desc

;
paragraphs.title: Every Locations Total sales with Promotion

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands), week
from marketing
where marketsize like 'Small'
group by locationid, week
;
paragraphs.title: Small Market performance

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands), week
from marketing
where marketsize like 'Medium'
group by locationid, week
;
paragraphs.title: Medium Market performance

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands), week
from marketing
where marketsize like 'Large'
group by locationid, week
;
paragraphs.title: Large Market performance

paragraphs.text:
select sum(salesinthousands), week, promotion
from marketing
group by week, promotion
;
paragraphs.title: Promotions Performance Overall

paragraphs.text:
select sum(salesinthousands), week, promotion
from marketing
group by week, promotion
;
paragraphs.title: Promotions Performance over the Month

paragraphs.text:
select sum(salesinthousands), week, promotion, marketsize
from marketing
group by week, promotion, marketsize
;

paragraphs.title: Promotions by Market Size

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands), week, promotion
from marketing
where promotion = 1 and marketsize like 'Large'
group by locationid, week, promotion
;
paragraphs.title: Promotion 1 in Large Market size

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands), week, promotion
from marketing
where promotion = 2 and marketsize like 'Large'
group by locationid, week, promotion
;
paragraphs.title: Promotion 2 in Large Market

paragraphs.text:
select locationid, sum(salesinthousands), week, promotion
from marketing
where promotion = 3 and marketsize like 'Large'
group by locationid, week, promotion

paragraphs.text:
select sum(salesinthousands), week, promotion, ageofstore
from marketing
group by week, promotion, ageofstore
;
